'''天主教弗赖堡總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Friburgensis}}；{{lang-de|Erzbistum Freiburg}}）是[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]在[[德國|德國]][[巴登-符騰堡州|巴登-符騰堡州]]設立的一個總教區。包括前[[巴登|巴登]]和[[霍亨索倫|霍亨索倫]]。弗赖堡總教區總主教又負責監管[[天主教美因茨教區|美因茨教區]]和[[天主教罗滕堡-斯图加特教区|天主教罗滕堡-斯图加特教区]]。

==現況==

總教區主教座堂設在[[弗赖堡主教座堂|弗赖堡主教座堂]]。2011年，有教友1,984,900人，佔轄區總人口41.6%、1,070個堂區、1,147名司鐸、243名執事、275名修士、1,591名修女。現任總主教為{{link-en|斯德望·布爾格爾|Stephan Burger}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 30.05.2014 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2014/05/30/0393/00891.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-08-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190809071316/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2014/05/30/0393/00891.html |archivedate=2019-08-09 |language=it |date=2014-05-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-de|伯多祿·比爾克霍費爾|Peter Birkhofer}}和{{link-de|克里斯蒂安·維爾茨|Christian Würtz}}<ref name="Vatican20180219">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 19.02.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/02/19/180219a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190809070946/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/02/19/180219a.html |archivedate=2019-08-09 |language=en |date=2018-02-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 26.04.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/04/26/190426b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190808165838/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/04/26/190426b.html |archivedate=2019-08-08 |language=en |date=2019-04-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為{{link-en|羅勃·措利奇|Robert Zollitsch}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 17.09.2013 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2013/09/17/0580/01277.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-08-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190809073915/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2013/09/17/0580/01277.html |archivedate=2019-08-09 |language=it |date=2013-09-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休輔理主教為{{link-de|保祿·韋爾萊 (主教)|Paul Wehrle (Bischof)|保祿·費德廉·韋爾萊}}、{{link-de|賴內爾·克盧格|Rainer Klug}}和{{link-de|伯爾納鐸·烏爾|Bernd Uhl|伯爾納鐸·若亞敬·烏爾}}<ref name="Vatican20180219" /><ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 30.07.2012 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2012/07/30/0443/01026.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-08-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190809075516/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2012/07/30/0443/01026.html |archivedate=2019-08-09 |language=it |date=2012-07-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 21.11.2013 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2013/11/21/0766/01729.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-08-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190809074821/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2013/11/21/0766/01729.html |archivedate=2019-08-09 |language=it |date=2013-11-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
1821年，弗赖堡總教區由康斯坦茨教區以及美因茨教區、斯特拉斯堡教區、沃爾姆斯教區和維爾茨堡教區的一部分組建而成。1827年，弗赖堡Bernhard Boll神父成為首任主教。今天，弗赖堡總教區堂區有所合併，但沒有關閉教堂。

